snippet.title: David Langer
snippet.description:
This channel's focus is the publishing of high-quality educational content on the 20% of Analytics and Data Science that drive 80% of ROI. 

I am an experienced hands-on analytics pro and professional trainer. I have taught hundreds of working professionals the foundational aspects of analytics and data science through my work with TDWI and Data Science Dojo. I have taught many thousands more via my YouTube tutorials.

The videos on this channel cover the complete Data Mining project lifecycle of data wrangling, data exploration, data cleaning, data visualization, data analysis, feature engineering, and machine learning. While not exclusive, this channel focuses primarily on the usage of Excel and R to conduct high-impact analyses of business data.
